<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">
        Financial peace as a spiritual practice.
      </h2>

      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-storehouse-500 pl-6 py-2 bg-storehouse-50/50 rounded-r-lg mb-10">
        <p class="text-xl font-display text-storehouse-700 italic">
          "Margin is an act of faith."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Living below your means creates space for the unpredictable:
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-storehouse-500 font-bold text-lg">1</span>
          <span class="text-slate-700">Space to respond when someone needs help</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-storehouse-500 font-bold text-lg">2</span>
          <span class="text-slate-700">Space to say yes to unexpected opportunity</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-storehouse-500 font-bold text-lg">3</span>
          <span class="text-slate-700">Space to weather job loss without panic</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-storehouse-500 font-bold text-lg">4</span>
          <span class="text-slate-700">Space to give generously when the moment calls</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Optimizing every dollar leaves no room for divine interruption. Building margin says: I trust that I don't need to control everything. I can hold my finances with open hands.
        </p>

        <p class="text-slate-900 font-medium">
          For many of us, this is worship.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
